text: Eleutherodactylidae is a family of frogs. They used to be a subfamily of Leptodactylidae. There are 801 frogs in the family. ==Genera== * Adelophryne Hoogmoed et Lescure, 1984. * Atopophrynus Lynch and Ruiz-Carranza, 1982. * Barycholos Heyer, 1969. * Diasporus Hedges, Duellman & Heinicke, 2008 * Dischidodactylus Lynch, 1979. * Eleutherodactylus Duméril and Bibron, 1841. * Euparkerella Griffiths, 1959. * Geobatrachus Ruthven, 1915. * Holoaden Miranda-Ribeiro, 1920. * Ischnocnema Reinhardt and Lütken, 1862 * Oreobates Jiménez de la Espada, 1872. * Phrynopus Peters, 1873. * Phyllonastes Heyer, 1977. * Phyzelaphryne Heyer, 1977. ==References== * Category:Frogs
title: Eleutherodactylidae
